widgets.label: Initialize timer & config ardour feedback
widgets.script:
send("/set_surface/bank_size", 0)
send("/set_surface/strip_types", 159)
send("/set_surface/feedback", 131)
send("/set_surface/gainmode", 0)
send("/set_surface/port", 0)
send("/strip/list")

setInterval(()=>{
var now = Date.now(),
    elapsed = now - get("start_time")

var f = "hour_fader"
set(f, elapsed / 1000 / 60)
set("clock", new Date().toLocaleTimeString())

}, 1000)

if (value) {

send("/strip/mute", 14, 0)
send("/strip/mute", 1, 1)
send("/strip/mute", 3, 1)
send("/strip/mute", 4, 1)
send("/strip/mute", 5, 1)

send("/strip/gain", 15, -20)

send("/strip/send/enable", 8, 1, 0)
send("/strip/send/enable", 8, 2, 0)

} else {

send("/strip/mute", 14, 1)

send("/strip/mute", 1, 0)
send("/strip/mute", 3, 0)
send("/strip/mute", 4, 0)
send("/strip/mute", 5, 0)

send("/strip/gain", 15, 0)

send("/strip/send/enable", 8, 1, 1)
send("/strip/send/enable", 8, 2, 1)

}

widgets.css:
border-right: 0.5rem solid var(--color-background);
border-left: 0.5rem solid var(--color-background)

widgets.label: Autotune
widgets.script:
var target='192.168.1.101:3819'
var address = "/strip/plugin/"
address += value ? "activate" : "deactivate"
send(target, address, @{parent.variables.n}, @{parent.variables.piid})
